Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.07,Default,Mob A,0,0,0,,Awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:13.16,Default,Mob A,0,0,0,,That's gotta be high-level\Nequipment... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.20,Default,Mob B,0,0,0,,And that crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.25,Default,Mob B,0,0,0,,It's from that achievement-focused\Nclan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:21.25,Default,Mob A,0,0,0,,What's someone like that doing\Nhere in the starting town?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:30.59,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}{M}I'd heard Hizutome-kun gives all\Nhis characters the same name,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.60,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I thought I'd be able to find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:37.93,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since there's no way a starting\Nplayer wouldn't come to this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.08,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Maybe I just missed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.81,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Give me something to enjoy here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}SLF{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.49,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,First, let's watch your patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.84,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's still a boss for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Its movements are easy to read,\Nand it won't have any
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.52,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,insta-kill moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:28.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I can beat this thing without taking a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.19,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Since even one hit would kill me anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I knew your durability was getting low,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,but did you just break on your first hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I was getting attached to\Nthese little guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A tough hide, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I've got something I'd like to try out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.81,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll make you into snake fillets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.94,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Screw Pi—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.62,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Poop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.41,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Well, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I might've underestimated this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Well, don't you look proud of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.13,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll have you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:41.93,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I've beaten trash games with\Nmechanics {\i1}way{\i0} cheaper than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.77,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A little poop-flinging won't\Nbe enough to get me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The poison deals me one\Ndamage every ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.52,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means I've got about four minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:05:00.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll need a reliable way to land\Ncriticals if I wanna make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.62,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Criticals in this game\Ndon't trigger at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}They seem to trigger when you\Nland an attack in an ideal way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.67,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}or hit an enemy in their weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:14.34,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This thing's covered in tough scales...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, the only weak point
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}has gotta be the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Still, it's hard to land a hit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.85,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.81,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll have to make my own weak point!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.23,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Screw Pierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, stack more hits on the wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The defensive properties of\Na wounded section change,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.62,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}allowing criticals to trigger there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:59.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, just hack away until\Nmy stamina gives out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:06.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Crud! I don't even know how\Nmuch HP this thing has!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Am I even gonna make it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:18.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Beating {\i1}Failia Chronicle {\i0}\Nmade me pretty cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"It's just a mass-appeal game for casuals..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.03,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"I can no-hit this thing easy,\Nno need for recovery items..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.41,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I was arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.97,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Flash Counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You're not gonna eat me that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You're gonna regret covering\Nme with your poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Screw Pierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I freaking did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.34,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You see that, poopsnake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I bet these dropped items\Ncould fetch some major dough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! I'm still running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.48,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Is that all the loot it dropped?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.32,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I didn't miss anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I gotta distribute my level-up points...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,No, there's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.78,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Just dump it all into stamina and agility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The minute I get to town,\NI'll buy an antidote...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wait, I dunno where the shops are!\NI won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'd better register my respawn point first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That'd be an inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But I don't know where\Nthat is either, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:15.64,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,You want to tame a dog-type\Nmonster, right, Mia?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.89,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.81,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not allowed to have pets in my apartment,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.31,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,{\an8}but I know you can have monsters\Nas pets in this game...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:26.44,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,So I hope you'll help me\Nout today, Yamamoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.90,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}After three months of trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.45,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally got the girl I'm crushing\Non to start playing {\i0}SLF{\i1} with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:39.46,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I've maneuvered myself into the\Nrole of the advice-giving veteran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:42.38,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let this chance pass me by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.75,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Um... Yamamoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.42,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:53.01,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Mia, game etiquette dictates that\Nwe don't use real-life names here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.26,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,We use character names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.14,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.31,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Reiji-kun, then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.85,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.36,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I even got her calling me by my given name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.27,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I owe you big, {\i0}SLF{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.94,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.32,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,A monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.28,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.70,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,It's got a character name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.83,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,It's not a monster, it's a player!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.50,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,So I shouldn't attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:24.17,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you PK, you'll end up with\Na skull in front of your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.17,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.51,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,But what's he running like that for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.97,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,I bet he got hit with that poison poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.18,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.43,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,You, over there! Sunraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.52,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Keep going straight! That white\Nbuilding there is the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:45.98,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,But your respawn point won't register\Nuntil you get into the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.02,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Thanks, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.11,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,You saw this a lot back\Nwhen the game started,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.66,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,before there was a whole\Nlot of fan documentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.79,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Players who got poisoned by that snake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.37,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,and had to run full-tilt into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.00,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Looking at the guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.75,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,I'm betting he's going for an agility build\Nand sold off his armor at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:11.26,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Reiji-kun, you sounded like a\Nreal veteran just now! I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.01,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.31,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Bluebird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.60,Default,NPC Receptionist,0,0,0,,You want to stay the night, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:28.23,Default,NPC Receptionist,0,0,0,,We provide places of sanctuary\Nwhere pioneers can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.02,Default,NPC Receptionist,0,0,0,,For instance—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.78,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Skip the explanation and rent me a dang bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.32,Default,NPC Receptionist,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.45,Default,NPC Receptionist,0,0,0,,I'll see if I can find you an free roo—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.32,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hur! Ry! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.66,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm down to my last HP, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.71,Default,NPC Receptionist,0,0,0,,Please proceed to room 102, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Right, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.83,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.26,Default,Window Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Respawn point registered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.26,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I made i—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:07.77,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.94,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,I made it just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.65,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,Still, I ended up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.41,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,I'm just glad I didn't lose my items.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.62,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,That player who told me where the inn was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.04,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to thank him\Nthe next time I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.87,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still... {\i0}SLF{\i1}, the god-tier game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.54,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pretty darn cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,All righty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:44.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Secondale here is my first\N{\i1}SLF{\i0} town experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll need a map, some recovery items,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:47.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,and new equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:52.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll need a powerful main weapon\Nto replace my Mercenary Twinblade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I wanna give this thing\Nall I've got, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hit the top player ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.16,Default,Mob A,0,0,0,,Who is that half-naked bird-man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.33,Default,Mob B,0,0,0,,A player?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.54,Default,Mob C,0,0,0,,Looks like a meme build or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.58,Default,Mob D,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.67,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe I'll buy clothes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll take the cheapest thing you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.67,Default,Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm not in this for the DEF.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:21.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}I just want the other players to\Nstop treating me like a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, the matching headpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.81,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Maybe I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.85,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh? A Goblin Hand Axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.77,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,{\an8}You expect me to buy this garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.86,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Show me your lineup of weapons, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.78,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.49,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Nothing too hot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:47.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,My Vorpal Choppers are way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:51.04,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Well, the Vorpal Chopper\Nis a pretty rare weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Oh, I was wondering about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:56.21,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,If you want something to top\Nthat, I'd have to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You can make me stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.63,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,If you bring me materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:04.81,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The path from Secondale to\Nthe third city, Thirdrema,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.60,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,passes through the Diremarsh Waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,There's a location within\Nit where ores can be mined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:17.78,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,So if I bring him some ore from\Nhere, he'll make me a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.41,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Another Stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:28.20,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Where's all the stupid ore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:33.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,He said I'd need five or six\Npieces to make a good weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But I've been swinging this pickax for\Nthirty minutes and I've only got two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.26,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Plus the marsh mud makes it hard to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:46.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And this pickax I bought to do the mining...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.52,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,is too darn heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.49,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Buzz off already. I've got stuff to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:13.29,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Okay. I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:17.21,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Since you weren't being aggressive,\NI thought we could coexist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But if you wanna be turned\Ninto materials that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.67,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll oblige!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,How do you like that, dummy frog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Now I'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.48,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Splitblade Leather armor I'm wearing now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}is made from Mud Frog Skin,\Nand it has slash resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:43.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it's pretty likely slash attacks\Nwon't work on froggy here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.62,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means my only options are\Nbludgeon and pierce attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for my Goblin Hand Axe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:54.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}whose edge is so blunt it actually\Ndeals bludgeon damage, to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,This is taking forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Why can't I run in this stupid marsh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.47,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The marsh slows down player\Nmovement significantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,forcing them into a walking state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:16.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,With a body shape like that, I bet it\Ncan't get off its back very easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:26.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That was so easy, it didn't even cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Back to mining, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's a pain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.95,Default,Mob Girl B,0,0,0,,{\an8}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm seeing more new players around...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.91,Default,Mob Girl A,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no way we can do it at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.87,Default,Mob Girl B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sure we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.04,Default,Mob Girl A,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.25,Default,Mob Girl B,0,0,0,,{\an8}We totally can! You can't be afraid to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll probably be seeing more soon,\Nwith summer break starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:45.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means it's only a matter of time\Nbefore the race for materials begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't wanna get caught up in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better collect as much\Nas I can, while I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.93,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,W-Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.94,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,You got quite a lot in just three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:03.32,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's gotta be enough to make\Nsomething pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:06.20,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Hold on. I'll bring up the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.53,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.66,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,You've got a Marshcoffin Fossil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:15.50,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember picking up that weird thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.50,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,I can use that to make this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hey, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll take it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And make it a double!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.55,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.59,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,I'll have them made right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.89,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,{\an8}There you are. A pair of Marsh Daggers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:42.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wow, god-tier weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:47.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And halving durability reduction\Nfor a time after a critical
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,makes them perfect for my playstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.87,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Make sure to find and bring\Nback even more materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.79,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Raising your weapons is part of our job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:57.87,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Raising" my weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.17,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Users of forging magic like me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.17,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,can do more than just make weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:06.26,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,We can also upgrade them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:11.13,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,But see, weapons are like\Nchildren to a blacksmith,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:16.10,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,so we prefer to say we "raise" them\Nto uncouth concepts like "upgrade."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}By the way, I gotta say,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.44,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}the NPC speech and mannerisms\Nhere are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.44,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}He's having a properly responsive\Nconversation with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}What kind of AI does this thing use?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.11,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, it's getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:35.41,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't leave\Ntown in armor like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.58,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:40.50,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Because nocturnal monsters\Nare dangerous, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:43.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Oh, the game's got that going on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.84,Default,NPC Shopkeep,0,0,0,,Sure, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That's what I told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But my penalty for dying's already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.80,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And I got some good info!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.93,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Time to use those\N"dangerous nocturnal monsters"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:03.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,to break in my new weapons\Nand pile on some levels!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.32,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:10.32,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've searched the entire beginners' area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.91,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Highest Strength Enchant Hell Flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.24,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Apocalypse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.25,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only remaining possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:25.79,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}is that he managed to defeat this snake\Nwithout stopping by town or dying
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.59,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}and headed for Secondale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.30,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Could a brand-new player really\Naccomplish such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.39,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Well, Hizutome-kun... probably could.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay... let's lay out what I've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.72,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, monster spawns change\Nbased on if it's day or night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:20.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Most nocturnal monsters are as aggressive\Nand dangerous as the weapons seller said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's helped me to make\Nprogress leveling up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}and to learn some new skills, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.52,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}this particular guy seems a\Nlittle too powerful, doesn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's totally broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:37.86,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This thing's movement and attacks are on a\Nwhole other level from the forest Goblins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.87,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got lots of HP, and incorporates\Nfeints into its fighting style
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:45.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}like it's been doing it all its life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the worst part of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Call Allies is supposed to\Nbe a weak monster ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.97,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had enough trouble with one,\Nbut look at all these!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:08.44,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even running away at full\Ntilt, I might not survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.19,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, man, are you losing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you enjoying this, or aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.17,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Is that all you got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:34.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Give me even more to enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:41.85,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been underestimating this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been telling myself,\N"god-tier games are pretty neat."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}You could even say I was getting into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:56.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this game...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i0}SLF{\i1} has way more to offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:05.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}On this day, in this instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:09.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I encountered the true {\i0}Shangri-La Frontier{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:18.09,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unique monster, Lycagon the\NNightslayer, encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.84,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Unique... monster?
